Try Two Spells:<br>
<br>
Horrifying Visage - On MA Tanks in PoP, I hit them with HV on incoming.  It really helps them keep aggro and regain it quickly if they lose it.<br>
<br>
Boggle - Its expensive but its fast and it works.<br>
<br>
and an AA ability<br>
<br>
Spell Casting Subtlety - Reduces aggro.<br>
