<br>
Anyone else getting this suspicion?<br>
<br>
Personally, I can understand the resists changes etc.  Sony doesn't want us chanters soloing Mini bosses, but the XP loss seems unnecessary.  I mean, why don't they have Necro pets taking 1/3 XP?  Not the charmed undead, the nearly unstoppable ones they always use... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub136.ezboard.com/beqenchantersrealm.showUserPublicProfile?gid=astyd>astyd</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 111<br> <font color=#330000>(5/19/03 12:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=176.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Charming and nerfage</span><hr size=1> <br>
I have had this discussion over at the Caster's Realm board.  There is a very vocal group of chanters who want a mass cancellation on June 1st.  I am not one of them.<br>
<br>
First, there are only 2 chanters that were effected by the MR nerf.  Beckon (was -10 adjust) and Command of Druzzil (was -50 adjust) are the only two spells affected.<br>
<br>
Second on the xp nerf, I have not seen it cause any issue if I do damage.  I generally throw in a cheap DoT to get my percentage of the kill.  Torment of Argli is very cheap and it does not ever break root, Torment of Scio is a bit more mana but does a lot more damage.<br>
<br>
Third, if you have been in a Planes group with a charmed mob you will notice the difference.  Even an unhasted mob will add to the DPS of the entire group in terms of damage.  That seems different than in the past.  As I recall, an all buffed Tier 2 mob does about 400 - 500 DPS.  AM3 Rangers and Rogues (not including Discs) do about 120 DPS.  Given that about 3 slots can be filled with them (1 Tank, 1 Slower, 1 Healer), you can see that this could be unbalancing.<br>
<br>
The major complaint is that Enchanters find it difficult to be the number 1 damage producer in Norrath.  I am actually quite okay with that, as I have never been a damage output machine.  I have been crowd control and buff/debuff.  Any DPS I add is gravy.  There is a complaint that Greater Fetter is a better crowd control spell.  In some cases that is true, but probably not for: small camps, caster mobs, and non-rootable mobs.<br>
<br>
Do I think that CoD got overnerfed?  Yes, I do.  I think the MR adjust should be somewhere between -10 and -30 (inclusive).  Do I believe that this nerf created a useless class?  No I do not.<br>
<br>
At the moment there are 3 classes that fall into the &quot;slower&quot; class that is basically a required class:<br>
<br>
Enchanter -<br>
Plusses: Mana Buffs, Hastes, Mezz, NDT, Aggro Buffing<br>
Minuses: Low DPS, No other buffs<br>
<br>
Shaman - <br>
Plusses: Melee Buffs, Backup Healer, Best Slow<br>
Minuses:  Root crowd control only, Low DPS<br>
<br>
Beastlord (65 only) -<br>
Plusses: Mana+HP Regen, High DPS<br>
Minuses: Buffs Pale against caster classes, Root crowd control only<br>
<br>
Given all of this, I do not have a big issue getting groups.  I don't have an issue charm soloing.<br>
<br>
Cames Houdini<br>
Coercer of Vazelle <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm11.showMessageRange?topicID=176.topic&start=21&stop=22>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm11.showPrevMessage?topicID=176.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm11.showNextMessage?topicID=176.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=176.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm11.threadControl?topicID=176.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm11.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=176.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm11.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=176.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub136.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="eqenchantersrealmfrm11